==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Compulsatory
<hw>Com*pul"sa*to*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Operating
with force; compelling; forcing; constraining; resulting from, or
enforced by, compulsion.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To recover of us, by strong hand⟦br⟧
And terms <qex>compulsatory</qex>, those foresaid lands.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Compulsion</ent>⟦br⟧
